4 05:22:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-opposes-using-anti-espionage-law-attack-its-business-environment-2024-03-04/</guid></item><item><title>中国将于3月5日至11日举行2024年全国人大会议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-hold-2024-parliamentary-meeting-march-5-11-2024-03-04/</link><description>中国全国人民代表大会发言人娄勤俭在周一的新闻发布会上告诉记者，中国全国人民代表大会（NPC）将于3月5日至11日在北京举行年度会议。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 04:14:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-hold-2024-parliamentary-meeting-march-5-11-2024-03-04/</guid></item><item><title>中国比亚迪新版畅销电动车价格低于前代</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-prices-new-version-best-selling-ev-lower-than-predecessor-2024-03-04/</link><description>随着全球最大汽车市场的价格战愈演愈烈，中国领先的电动汽车 (EV) 制造商比亚迪周一推出了其最畅销汽车的新版本，价格低于其停产前身的最终价格。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 03:12:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-prices-new-version-best-selling-ev-lower-than-predecessor-2024-03-04/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾进行海上巡逻以检查中国科考船的存在</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-conducts-marine-patrols-check-presence-chinese-research-ships-2024-03-04/</link><description>菲律宾周一部署一艘海岸警卫队船只在该国北部和东部海域执行为期两周的巡逻任务，以加强其海上存在，并对在宾汉隆起发现的中国科考船进行检查。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 02:05:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-conducts-marine-patrols-check-presence-chinese-research-ships-2024-03-04/</guid></item><item><title>韩国和美国军队开始针对朝鲜威胁的年度演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/south-korea-us-troops-kick-off-annual-drills-over-north-threats-2024-03-04/</link><description>官员们表示，韩国和美国军队周一开始了春季演习，参加的部队人数是去年的两倍，因为这两个盟国寻求更好地应对朝鲜日益增加的核威胁和导弹威胁。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 02:01:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/south-korea-us-troops-kick-off-annual-drills-over-north-threats-2024-03-04/</guid></item><item><title>等待美联储线索，美元波动；比特币创两年新高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-eases-fed-clues-awaited-bitcoin-hits-2-year-high-2024-03-04/</link><description>周一，受美国国债收益率走低的压力，美元窄幅波动，交易者等待更重要的经济数据，以获取有关美联储降息时机的新线索。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 01:49:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-eases-fed-clues-awaited-bitcoin-hits-2-year-high-2024-03-04/</guid></item><item><title>日经指数引领亚洲走高，未来一周活动精彩纷呈</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-03-04/</link><description>亚洲股市周一走强，日经指数再创新高，投资者准备迎接充满央行事件和重大数据的一周，这些数据将完善市场对利率何时开始下降的押注。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 00:22:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-03-04/</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚警告东南亚“胁迫行动”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/australia-welcomes-southeast-asia-leaders-with-fresh-maritime-security-funding-2024-03-03/</link><description>澳大利亚周一表示，印度太平洋和东南亚国家正面临严重的国防威胁，因为在墨尔本与地区领导人举行的峰会上，澳大利亚为与东盟国家的海上安全项目拨出了更多资金。</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 23:48:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/australia-welcomes-southeast-asia-leaders-with-fresh-maritime-security-funding-2024-03-03/</guid></item><item><title>美国资助法案阻止中国从战略石油储备购买石油</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/us-funding-bill-blocks-china-buying-oil-strategic-petroleum-reserve-2024-03-03/</link><description>国会领导人周日公布的美国资助立法中的一项措施将阻止中国从战略石油储备购买石油。</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 23:34:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/us-funding-bill-blocks-china-buying-oil-strategic-petroleum-reserve-2024-03-03/</guid></item><item><title>早盘：全球情绪高涨，中国2024年计划迫在眉睫</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-03-03/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 21:48:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-03-03/</guid></item><item><title>泰国协助将900名诈骗受害者从缅甸转移到中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thailand-facilitates-transfer-900-scam-victims-myanmar-china-2024-03-03/</link><description>泰国总理斯雷塔·塔维辛 (Srettha Thavisin) 周日表示，泰国上周帮助将被困在缅甸边境城镇诈骗中心的约 900 名中国公民转移回中国。</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 12:23:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thailand-facilitates-transfer-900-scam-victims-myanmar-china-2024-03-03/</guid></item><item><title>马来西亚称 MH370 失踪 10 年后必须继续搜寻</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/malaysia-says-mh370-search-must-go-10-years-after-plane-vanished-2024-03-03/</link><description>马来西亚交通部长周日表示，随着该航班在世界上最大的航空谜团之一失踪十周年的临近，马来西亚正在推动重新搜寻马来西亚航空 MH370 航班。</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 12:19:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/malaysia-says-mh370-search-must-go-10-years-after-plane-vanished-2024-03-03/</guid></item></channel></rss>